      • convert

        public parser.token.Token convert(parser.token.Token token)
                           throws exceptions.MissingLeftParenthesisException
        Method used to implement overloading. It will used the stack to decide what on earth the given token's type.
        参数:
        token - the token to be analyze
        返回:
        the token after converting
        抛出:
        exceptions.MissingLeftParenthesisException - if the expression miss left parenthesis
